odrive-linux (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * GTK4/Libadwaita Manager with onboarding wizard, mount management,
    folder sync rules, backup jobs, trash, encryptor folders, advanced
    agent settings, log viewer, and tray indicator.
  * Rust CLI for status, sync/unsync, mount, share-link, and packaging
    payload generation.
  * Optional Nautilus right-click integration (separate package).
  * Optional Dolphin Qt6/KF6 integration (separate package).

 -- Keith Vassallo <keith@icemalta.com>  Wed, 06 May 2026 17:30:50 +0100
